\title{Exclusive Sectorial Search Command}
\description{
An \link[R6:R6Class]{R6} class that configures an exclusive sectorial search
in \pkg{nitro}.

Exclusive sectorial searches subdivide the entire tree into
non-overlapping sectors and perform branch swapping within each. The
number of sectors can be specified as a fixed value or a range. This
wraps the \code{sectsch} TNT command with the \code{xss} subcommand.
}
\details{
\subsection{Default values}{\tabular{ll}{
   Parameter \tab Default \cr
